# Copy to .env (gitignored) to change what `make generate` builds.
#
# These are build switches, not secrets. Nothing here is confidential: a bundle
# identifier and a Team ID ship inside every distributed app and can be read
# straight out of an .ipa. The things that must stay private are your signing
# certificate's private key and your App Store Connect API key (.p8), and
# neither of those belongs in this repository.

# Compile the battles feature in. It builds for the simulator with no account at
# all, because simulators do not enforce entitlements; running it on a real
# device or shipping it needs a paid Apple Developer account and the CloudKit
# container from docs/DEVELOPMENT.md. Leave it false to build Zwäg without
# battles: no CloudKit, no iCloud entitlement, no Battles tab.
#
# Toggling this rewrites the entitlements file, so run `make clean` afterwards.
ZWAEG_BATTLES=false
